rator": "\n", "text": "SYNETHETIX  LABS  -  OFFICIAL  HOLIDAY  CALENDAR  2026  \nOverview:  >  This  document  lists  the  mandatory  office  closure  dates  for  all  \nemployees\n \nof\n \nSynthetix\n \nLabs\n \nfor\n \nthe\n \ncalendar\n \nyear\n \n2026.\n \nGazetted  Holidays  (Office  Closed):  \n\u25cf  New  Year's  Day:  January  1,  2026  (Thursday)  \u25cf  Republic  Day:  January  26,  2026  (Monday)  \u25cf  Holi:  March  4,  2026  (Wednesday)  \u25cf  Eid-ul-Fitr:  March  21,  2026  (Saturday)  \u25cf  Independence  Day:  August  15,  2026  (Saturday)  \u25cf  Gandhi  Jayanti:  October  2,  2026  (Friday)  \u25cf  Diwali:  November  8,  2026  (Sunday)  \u25cf  Christmas  Day:  December  25,  2026  (Friday)  \nNote:  For  any  holidays  falling  on  a  Sunday  (like  Diwali),  the  following  Monday  will  \nnot\n \nbe\n \na\n \nholiday\n \nunless\n \nspecifically\n \nnotified\n \nby\n \nHR.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 813, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}}}